
  x Group support
    x Advanced "Departmental" group support
      o Roles applied in the group should be valid also for the group object
    x Simple Group plugin to "emulate" userFolderWithGroups
      x Groups in groups

  o A search method on each plugin would enable plugins to make efficient
    searches instead of returning all users.

  o A method of transferring users and groups from UserFolderWithGroups
